{"tid":2425703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★支拜effect】美國伊州擬禁售暴力遊戲     成年人亦受規範","createTime":"2021-02-27T13:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T14:02:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f32eea45d91dfd7f111a0a8f108b5c4fc0fac7ca","tid":2425703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/5bb5ff072400005000981947.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F5bb5ff072400005000981947.jpeg&h=08fa0428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國伊州有眾議員計劃倡議禁止全州銷售暴力遊戲，即成年人也將無法在伊州內購買任何被界定為有暴力傾向的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國伊州在 2012 年的法律的修正案，該州法律目前禁止零售商向未成年人出售某些暴力遊戲，而眾議員 Marcus C. Evans, Jr. 打算倡議禁止銷售所有暴力遊戲。他在上周五（19 日）提交相關文件，以減少芝加哥劫車和暴力犯罪事件的數量為由訂立 3531 號法案。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據 Marcus C. Evans, Jr. 擬交的法案所述，允許用戶或玩家控制遊戲中的角色，並鼓勵其永久維持人與人之間的暴力，如殺死、以任何方式造成角色嚴重身體傷害，或心理傷害等，即屬暴力遊戲。而違反法律，出售或出租暴力遊戲者將被處以 1,000 美元（約港幣 HKD$ 7750）的罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/02/27/illinois-rep-violent-games/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F02%2F27%2Fillinois-rep-violent-games%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=372c27b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/02/27/illinois-rep-violent-games/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"f8f4f097e755a3ff534883ae5bc04a377731a106","tid":2425703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:37:42.000Z","msg":"no more gta<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc771d44c7713cc9202fc806a061aaf6a7d0d5b9","tid":2425703,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"成年人---no sex、 no game，no AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15776d15a97c4c760cc8d66322571f8c8ba05d37","tid":2425703,"uid":113187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"抵制不良游戏，拒绝盗版游戏。注意自我保护，谨防受骗上当。适度游戏益脑，沉迷游戏伤身。合理安排时间，享受健康生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14a3f23973bb64b4287a43525b26c981820b947","tid":2425703,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"US soon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://q4a2z2v6.rocketcdn.me/wp-content/uploads/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-%E6%93%BA%E9%8E%AE-%E2%94%82-%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A%E6%89%98%E7%BC%BD%E5%8C%96%E7%B7%A3%E3%80%82-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fq4a2z2v6.rocketcdn.me%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%2593%25BA%25E9%258E%25AE-%25E2%2594%2582-%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25B0%259A%25E6%2589%2598%25E7%25BC%25BD%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E3%2580%2582-1.jpg&h=29e6b58f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fae38866261d113ffbb1f3ba2f5b8b7170230b7b","tid":2425703,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"同時民主黨在加州鼓勵搶劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809cfbc616db3188f9037f5aca261490f578b91e","tid":2425703,"uid":30825